OL,3,CMan jailed after detectives use DNA to
OL,4,Clink him to Tesco ram raid attempt
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for two years
OL,7,Fafter DNA evidence linked him to an
OL,8,Fattempted ram raid at a Tesco
OL,9,Fsupermarket in Gloucestershire last
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FJack Bradley, 25, of HMP Hewell,
OL,13,Fpleaded guilty to burglary with intent
OL,14,Fto steal.
OL,16,FThe incident occurred in the early
OL,17,Fhours of 6 December 2023, when a group
OL,18,Fof men used a Mercedes 4x4 to try to
OL,19,Fforce their way into the Tesco
OL,20,FSuperstore on Church Road in Bishop
OL,21,FCleeve's.
