OL,6,FCCTV footage showed the group clearing
OL,7,Fthe foyer of Christmas wreaths,
OL,8,Fdisplay shelves, and baskets before
OL,9,Framming metal shutters with the
OL,10,Fvehicle in an attempt to access the
OL,11,Fmain supermarket.
OL,13,FStaff were working inside at the time,
OL,14,Fbut the group left without stealing
OL,15,Fanything.
OL,17,FRepairs cost nearly #80,000, and the
OL,18,Fstore had to close for the day,
OL,19,Fresulting in an estimated #120,000
OL,20,Floss in sales and wages.
