OL,3,CMan jailed after detectives use DNA to
OL,4,Clink him to Tesco ram raid attempt
OL,6,FBradley became a suspect after his DNA
OL,7,Fwas found on a tissue left in the
OL,8,Fsupermarket car park and inside a
OL,9,Fstolen van abandoned near the scene.
OL,11,FForensic analysis of the van revealed
OL,12,Fhis DNA on the steering wheel, gear
OL,13,Fstick, handbrake, a vape, and a
OL,14,Fscrewdriver.
OL,16,FWhen interviewed by police in February
OL,17,F2024, Bradley admitted he planned to
OL,18,Ftake a safe if the raid had succeeded.
OL,19,FHe was already serving a three-year
OL,20,Fsentence for unrelated burglary
OL,21,Foffences at the time of his arrest.
