OL,3,CMan jailed after detectives use DNA to
OL,4,Clink him to Tesco ram raid attempt
OL,6,FPC Hancock, the investigating officer,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I am pleased that Bradley has
OL,8,Fbeen sentenced as his actions on 6
OL,9,FDecember last year had a huge impact
OL,10,Fon those involved. It affected the
OL,11,Fcommunity of Bishop's Cleeve as well
OL,12,Fas Tesco and its employees.
OL,14,F"This would've been a very frightening
OL,15,Fexperience for the members of staff
OL,16,Fwho were in the building at the time
OL,17,Fof the attempted ram raid."
